item.title: Ralph Lauren Aviator Sunglasses
item.dc:creator: rockystef
item.content:encoded:
This is a demo product. Naming his brand after a sport that embodied a world of classic style, Ralph Lauren created Polo Ralph Lauren in 1967 as a label initially selling men’s ties. The label quickly grew and redefined American style with their signature preppy menswear. The now iconic Polo Ralph Lauren polo shirt was introduced in 1972 in twenty four colours and instantly became a classic, offering both quality construction and wide variety. Interested in longevity, timelessness and style, Polo Ralph Lauren signifies lasting American menswear that builds upon its rich history of design with seasonal collections that offer effortless style. Sunglasses by Polo Ralph Lauren
  • Metal frames with double bridge
  • Adjustable silicone nose pads for added comfort
  • Reflective lenses
  • Straight arms with curved temple tips for a secure fit
  • Total UV protection
  • Colour of protective case may vary
LOOK AFTER ME Wipe Light Marks With A Soft Cloth ABOUT ME Frame: 100% Metal, Lens: 100% Plastic. FC3, General purpose sunglasses, high protection against sunglare. Not for use as eye protection against mechanical impact. Not suitable for driving in twilight or at night. Do not use abrasive detergents or sprays. Comes with a soft pouch case.
